sub_title: Senior Researcher/Quantum Technologies team lead at Aramco
summary:
A versatile mathematical physicists with 10+ years of working experience with a keen interest in advanced methods in seismic data processing and imaging, as well as applications of quantum computing in the energy business.

i particularly enjoy working at the boundary between academia and the industry to bring the latest advances in science to the in-house technology portfolio.
